⚖️ But here’s the important correction

We don’t each get our own separate reality
We share one world, but:

We carry different maps of it

Think of it like:

* Same terrain 🌍
* Different maps 🗺️

Some maps overlap → easy communication
Some don’t → feels like “different species”

